{"meta":{"updateDate":1755117017717,"pPcc":"SAT#P","questionId":"09e5e4d3","skill_cd":"P.B.","score_band_range_cd":4,"skill_desc":"Nonlinear equations in one variable and systems of equations in two variables ","createDate":1755117017717,"program":"SAT","primary_class_cd_desc":"Advanced Math","ibn":"","external_id":"3ba3f345-5069-44e0-84d8-8513595b8722","primary_class_cd":"P","uId":"ddc64683-9b31-4936-ac49-f1b0866596b4","difficulty":"M"},"source":"modern","detail":{"type":"mcq","stem":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If <math alttext=\"StartFraction 42 Over x EndFraction equals 7 x\"><mrow>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<mfrac>\n\t\t\t<mn>42</mn>\n\t\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t</mfrac>\n\t</mrow>\n\t<mo>=</mo>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<mn>7</mn>\n\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t</mrow>\n</mrow>\n</math>, what is the value of <math alttext=\"7 x squared\"><mrow>\n\t<mn>7</mn>\n\t<msup>\n\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t<mn>2</mn>\n\t</msup>\n</mrow>\n</math>?</p>","keys":["2917411f-d05f-467b-9545-371067e9655a"],"answerOptions":[{"id":"d17d1f6a-9f1b-4d32-b3ef-1b59e3d78e25","content":"<p><math alttext=\"6\"><mn>6</mn>\n</math></p>"},{"id":"98d7fdda-1e30-4abf-8edc-8e63f8aba501","content":"<p><math alttext=\"7\"><mn>7</mn>\n</math></p>"},{"id":"2917411f-d05f-467b-9545-371067e9655a","content":"<p><math alttext=\"42\"><mn>42</mn>\n</math></p>"},{"id":"d83e9902-a639-4b42-910f-7b25aa9ba4b0","content":"<p><math alttext=\"294\"><mn>294</mn>\n</math></p>"}],"rationale":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice C is correct. Multiplying both sides of the given equation by <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi></math> yields <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"42 equals 7 x squared\"><mn>42</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>. Therefore, the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"7 x squared\"><mn>7</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math> is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"42\"><mn>42</mn></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice A is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice B is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice D is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>","externalid":"3ba3f345-5069-44e0-84d8-8513595b8722","correct_answer":["C"]}}